I have your book.


34
00:04:58.495 --> 00:05:00.097
爱德华，那是我的书。给它回来。
Edward, that's my book. Give it back.


35
00:05:01.866 --> 00:05:04.493
-还给我!-爱德华，马上住手!
- Give it back! - Edward, stop this at once!


36
00:05:04.535 --> 00:05:06.028
夏洛特。
Charlotte.


37
00:05:06.070 --> 00:05:07.672
请。
Please.


38
00:05:09.907 --> 00:05:12.409
