There does seem to be some validity to the claim that dates back 80 years, but there is nothing on record that can't be changed in our favor.


52
00:09:39.410 --> 00:09:41.670
有人试过和他们谈判吗?
Has anyone tried to negotiate with them?


53
00:09:41.712 --> 00:09:45.240
他们是吉普赛人,谢默斯。
They're Gypsies, Seamus.


54
