That can't be allowed to happen.


58
00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:11.075
在这个房间里，我们都有可能失去一些东西，所以我的建议是别在这里说。
We all have something to lose in this room, so what I'm suggesting stays in this room.


59
00:10:11.442 --> 00:10:14.136
夏洛特，爱德华，你们走吧。你去。走,走。
Charlotte, Edward, off you go. Off you go. Go, go.


