一个警告。他这种人在这里不受欢迎。
A warning. His kind aren't welcome 'round here.


74
00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:25.588
一定要把这些和她一起埋了。
Make sure you bury these with her.


75
00:14:25.630 --> 00:14:27.189
