银。值一大笔钱。
Silver. Worth a pretty penny.


77
00:14:30.100 --> 00:14:33.203
没有任何价值。就死亡。
There's no worth in it. Just death.


78
00:14:41.311 --> 00:14:42.513
让他们离开我的视线!
Get 'em outta my sight!


79
00:14:43.380 --> 00:14:44.674
来吧!
Come on!


80
00:14:48.653 --> 00:14:49.386
把他放在那里。
Put him there.


81
